2007-10-20  Jun Yan  <jyan@stat.uconn.edu>

	* Release 0.2-2 includes goodness-of-fit test for comparing
	two models which are different only in the specification of one
	coefficient: time-varying or time-independent.

2007-09-28  Jun Yan  <jyan@stat.uiowa.edu>

	* Release 0.2-1 includes a test version of smoothing the 
	time varying coefficient estimate with kernel methods.
	

2007-06-14  Jun Yan  <jyan@stat.uiowa.edu>

	* Release 0.1-2 is for Arthur Allignol <arthur.allignol@gmail.com>
	to test with his data; it is almost ready for public release. 

	* Nonparametric significance test, parametric constant fit, and 
	goodness-of-fit tests for constant fit are available. The tests
	implemented are integral test and bootstrap test.

	* The ci.plot function is documented.

